## Bugs Fixed During Verification

1. **FL Engine dtype error** — `torch.randn_like` failed on integer params (e.g. BatchNorm `num_batches_tracked`). Fixed by skipping non-float params in DP noise injection.
2. **Missing numpy import** — [blockchain/audit_trail.py](file:///e:/VS%20Code/cyber/blockchain/audit_trail.py) used `np.mean` but only imported numpy in `__main__`. Moved to module level.
3. **Plotly 8-digit hex colors** — `f"{color}20"` produced invalid 8-char hex. Added [hex_to_rgba()](file:///e:/VS%20Code/cyber/app.py#32-37) helper converting all 11 occurrences to proper [rgba()](file:///e:/VS%20Code/cyber/app.py#32-37) format.

## How to Run

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install torch torch-geometric networkx streamlit plotly pandas numpy scikit-learn matplotlib

# Run integration test
python test_all.py

# Launch dashboard
streamlit run app.py
```
